Hotel E Mail Blast
(August 24, 2001)

New York Road Runners and our partner, Total Travel Management is pleased
to offer New York City Marathoners special discounted hotel rates and
Continental Airlines airfare for your trip to New York this November.

To take advantage of this special offer, please contact Total Travel
Management today at (516) 222-9229 or via email at ttmny@ix.netcom.com.
This is a very busy week in New York so please make your reservations
early!

