Airline Discounts
Total Travel Management has arranged special airline discount on
Continental Airlines, the official airline of the New York City Marathon:
10% off lowest available fare at least 60 days prior to travel
5% off lowest available fare within 60 days prior to travel

To make reservations, please call Continental's Meeting Works at
800.468.7022. Please reference UFWOT4 Code ZK9Q or contact Total Travel
Management to book your special fare.

If you do not live in a city served by Continental Airlines, discounts are
available on other airlines:

AIRLINE 		DOMESTIC CODE		INTERNATIONAL CODE

American Airlines: 	AN#29H1AM			AN#29H1AM
Delta Airlines: 	#175940A 			#175941A

Please call Total Travel Management with any questions.

For a downloadable and printable version of this information, please log
onto nycmarathon.org.

